'''Muḥmmad Lmuxtar iwis n Ɛli iwis n Ḥmad asusi u [[iliɣ]]''' ittussan s '''Riḍa allah''' nɣ '''Lmuxtar ssusi''', ilul g usggas n 1900 [[Ḍaṛt Tlalit]], immt g usggas n 1963 [[Ḍaṛt Tlalit]]. iga yan urgaz n tussna d tmassant (lɛilm); iga anmzray (ar icnubbuc f [[Amzruy|umzruy]]), ig argaz n [[Taskla|tskla]] ig ula argaz n [[Asgd|usgd]], ig ula amɣnas d unzbay amɣribi. 

== Tudrt nns ==
Ilul ɣ [[Iliɣ]] tama n [[Tafrawt]] gr taqbilt n [[Ayt wafqqa]]. Ntan a izwarn s tamawast n lawqaf d usgd ɣ 1956 ayliɣ tffaɣ [[Fransa]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]]. Immut ɣ yan ungas n tmubilt gr [[Sṭṭat]] d [[Tigmmi Tumlilt|Tigmi Tumlil]] aylliɣ d yurri ɣ [[Mrrakc]]. 

